HEADWORD: Befoul
<hw>Be*foul"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Befouled</conjf> <pr>(<?/)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
